{"type": "article", "id": 25644, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-19T07:12:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 26389, "name": "MAYO Clinic"}, {"id": 26390, "name": "Kram/Weisshaar"}, {"id": 26391, "name": "Kommigraphics Design Studio"}, {"id": 26392, "name": "北川大辅"}, {"id": 26393, "name": "Lunar Europe"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125943wVULKkfr34n6p2SP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Mogura &amp; Ishi by Nendo</h2>\n<p>这是日本设计工作室 Nendo 为意大利品牌 De Padova 设计的灯和桌子，在极简设计中带有活泼的趣味。灯罩像是从一个鸟笼中“挖”开了一个洞，灯泡恰好固定在洞的中间，打破了原本规整的空间，非常生动。而茶几的底座是 11 块高低和大小不一的木块，上面是最普通的玻璃，就像是石头与河流的关系。木块是用柏木手工制作的，每一个都不一样，自然的纹路很有装饰性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123402k9myXYoDVwi5leaM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123402fv5k2JQTtFxLBseH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70609756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123403MhFwvois5k6eS9LG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123403GBTWnRIJL50fMlkv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123404BbO9fIwTPSWd4jnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70609756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021234042nNzOj9t51vdLTfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70609756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>HOVR by MAYO Clinic</h2>\n<p>这个挂在桌下的脚踏板帮助久坐的人燃烧卡路里以及血液循环，它使用了类似书包肩带作为支撑结构，保持了一定的弹性并能收缩长短，让两只脚一直晃动。可以连接上 app 来监测消耗的热量。它还有另一款是完全独立的，让坐在沙发上的人也能活动起来。设计者芝加哥的工作室 MAYO Clinic，产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/hovr-unconsciously-burn-more-calories-at-work#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123405xqAd62a8eHCpMVN1.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123405Z8QPiDRqKfWrXuG2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123406D94drG8asuVXyiEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9075\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123407JteZ5LDg8Tco7Oa9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123407bchAyoEsPI0M4VrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123408c6jOFXwQTroGuVdh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>razor-thin table by Kram/Weisshaar </h2>\n<p>这张餐桌隐藏了电路系统，可以调整桌面特定区域的温度，让准备食材、加热到吃饭都在一张桌子上。它使用了一种 SapienStone 的陶瓷材料，让桌子的厚度只有 6 毫米，从侧面看，餐具就像悬浮在半空中了，简约现代。设计者来自团队 Kram/Weisshaar ，产品刚刚在米兰设计周上展出。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123408Vadm5CtHgy3ecZ60.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123409CJBtHTNK2D5dW0xm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123409jtvOU04LwIrWBX65.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123409zFcIGZnEKH7BQSr1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123410NnO0GiztfpyHMTmg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>reflect 系列 by 北川大辅</h2>\n<p>这是日本设计师北川大辅在米兰设计周上推出的“反应系列”。他展出了 5 组常见的家具，在看似普通的外形中拥有细微的设计感。比如月亮灯是让灯光反射到墙面上，从正面看像是月食现象。正方形的独立沙发只有两边有靠背，围成了一个三角形的空间，给人蜷缩的安全感。花瓶则刻意做出了一排凹槽，可以让插在上面的花更整齐。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123410MnraXLOoscy1hR6u.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123411HqQvt79AEIg4CbzD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123411foqSdHpgyEtj4i7Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123412EKVq5DcyuCYtG8mj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123412XT8oA5BuqQ4GZ6Rn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123412bSHPLrfM59g7nKdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Tera by Lunar Europe</h2>\n<p>这是一款智能健身垫，使用了来自丹麦 Kvadrat 的羊毛面料。它可以连接上 TERA app 来检测施加的压力变化，以监督动作的标准。此外，垫子上均匀分布着小的三角纹路是一个 LED 照明系统。它可以引导当身体与垫子接触时的动作。<a href=\"http://tera.lunar-europe.com/Solution.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123413ZgelxVatYcI0pAuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123413cZ9D87uNQj4LhiHJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123414MZuGzDLgXn2p5dK4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123414EnDMO8uQZF1zdfUL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021234153gpwk091Uu6OyPlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Hamas Drink by Kommigraphics Design Studio</h2>\n<p>夏天快到了，看到清凉的汽水或果汁总是忍不住买一瓶。这组来自希腊的酒精饮料Yamas 加入了柠檬、橙子和酸橙三种不同的果汁，它们被画成了黄色、橙色和绿色的水果出现在瓶身的椅子上，有轻微的摇动和洒出果汁的感觉，很诱人。白色的竖高瓶子就给人一种清新的感受，文字和图案一律采用蓝色，用漫画的风格画出了近似于酒吧的高脚椅，是适合年轻人的包装。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123415lFQBwVcLC6WN9ugy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212341602IQl1pt8foFbr5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123416CL9cusUwFxbh7VEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123417dgbSa5EJCIWeZN0V.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021234179YLylxZXQ1JSzkCW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021234184T9MzvloDm0OAZBi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}